OL,7,FSecondary school-aged girls in Wales
OL,8,Fhave much higher rates of self-
OL,9,Freported problematic social media use
OL,10,Fthan boys, research shows.
OL,12,FThe differences were most pronounced
OL,13,Fin Year 9 and Year 10, with one in
OL,14,Ffive girls reporting their own
OL,15,Fproblematic use compared with one in
OL,16,F10 boys.
