OL,7,FPublic Health Wales and Cardiff
OL,8,FUniversity analysed data from the 2023
OL,9,FThe School Health Research Network
OL,10,Fstudent health and wellbeing secondary
OL,11,Fschool survey.
OL,13,FIt asked young people aged between 11
OL,14,Fand 16 a series of questions about
OL,15,Ftheir social media use and whether
OL,16,Fthey had neglected other activities in
OL,17,Ffavour of social media.
