OL,7,FIt found that 21% of girls in Year 10
OL,8,Fand 20% of Year 9 reported the highest
OL,9,Frate of problematic social media use,
OL,10,Fcompared with 10% and 9% of boys
OL,11,Frespectively.
OL,13,FThe overall figure for Wales is 17%
OL,14,Ffor girls and 9% for boys.
OL,16,FAs well as the difference between
OL,17,Fgenders, there was also a gap between
OL,18,Ffamilies in differing economic
OL,19,Fsituations.
