OL,7,FGirls from low and middle affluence
OL,8,Fhouseholds reported scores for
OL,9,Fproblematic social media use at 20%
OL,10,Fand 19% respectively, significantly
OL,11,Fhigher than the boys in the same
OL,12,Fgroups who were at 12% and 10%
OL,13,Frespectively.
OL,15,FDr Emily van de Venter, consultant in
OL,16,Fhealth improvement for Public Health
OL,17,FWales, said "We have seen a lot of
OL,18,Fdiscussion about the problematic use
OL,19,Fof social media by young people in
OL,20,Frecent months.
