OL,7,F"Social media can provide benefits
OL,8,Fthrough greater connectivity, but a
OL,9,Fconcerning number of young people are
OL,10,Freporting negative impacts on their
OL,11,Frelationships, engagement with hobbies
OL,12,Fand difficulties in limiting their
OL,13,Ftime using it.
