OL,7,F"While we are currently working on our
OL,8,Funderstanding of the impact of social
OL,9,Fmedia use on young people, we would
OL,10,Frecommend that all young people have a
OL,11,F'balanced diet' of activities,
OL,12,Fincluding making time for hobbies,
OL,13,Fsocialising with friends, physical
OL,14,Factivity and school work, alongside
OL,15,Fthings like social media or online
OL,16,Fgaming.
