OL,7,FDr Kelly Morgan, director of the
OL,8,FSchool Health Research Network, added:
OL,9,F"By including these questions in our
OL,10,Fnational survey we're able to gain an
OL,11,Funderstanding of how young people use
OL,12,Fsocial media, and explore how
OL,13,Fexperiences vary across different
OL,14,Fgroups.
OL,16,F"This allows us to build a much richer
OL,17,Funderstanding of how this issue
OL,18,Frelates to wider health behaviours."
